## 4.3

依据边界条件与正交性

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_0^L \frac{m\omega_i^2}{EI} W_j(x) W_i(x) \, dx &= \int_0^L \frac{\partial^4 W_i(x)}{\partial x^4} W_j(x) \, dx \\
&= \left. \frac{\partial^3 W_i(x)}{\partial x^3} W_j(x) \right|_0^L - \int_0^L \frac{\partial^3 W_i(x)}{\partial x^3} \frac{\partial W_j(x)}{\partial x} \, dx \\
&= -\int_0^L \frac{\partial^3 W_i(x)}{\partial x^3} \frac{\partial W_j(x)}{\partial x} \, dx \\
&= -\left. \frac{\partial^2 W_i(x)}{\partial x^2} \frac{\partial W_j(x)}{\partial x} \right|_0^L + \int_0^L \frac{\partial^2 W_i(x)}{\partial x^2} \frac{\partial^2 W_j(x)}{\partial x^2} \, dx \\
&= \frac{k}{EI} \left. \frac{\partial W_i(x)}{\partial x} \frac{\partial W_j(x)}{\partial x} \right|_{x = L} + \int_0^L \frac{\partial^2 W_i(x)}{\partial x^2} \frac{\partial^2 W_j(x)}{\partial x^2} \, dx
\end{align*}
$$

同理

$${\left. {\frac{k}{{EI}}\frac{{\partial {W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}\frac{{\partial {W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}} \right|_{x = L}} + \int_0^L {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}\frac{{{\partial ^2}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{\rm{d}}x} = \frac{{m\omega _j^2}}{{EI}}\int_0^L {{W_i}\left( x \right){W_j}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x}$$

所以

$$
\left( {\omega _i^2 - \omega _j^2} \right)\int_0^L {{W_i}\left( x \right)m{W_j}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} = 0
$$

当$\omega _i^2 \ne \omega _j^2$,则有

$$\int_0^L {{W_i}\left( x \right)m{W_j}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} = 0$$
div.p: 依据边界条件与正交性

## 4.4

$$
\begin{align*}
\left\langle M\left[ W_1 \right], W_1 \right\rangle &\approx 0.517 mL \\
\left\langle M\left[ W_2 \right], W_2 \right\rangle &\approx 0.505 mL \\
\left\langle M\left[ W_3 \right], W_3 \right\rangle &\approx 0.503 mL
\end{align*}
$$

则

$${W_i}\left( x \right) = {c_i}\left( {\sin {\alpha _i}x - \frac{{\sin {\alpha _i}L}}{{\sinh {\alpha _i}L}}\sinh {\alpha _i}x} \right),\;\;i = 1,2,3 \dots$$

其中

$$
\begin{align*}
c_1 &= \frac{1}{\sqrt{0.517mL}} \\
c_2 &= \frac{1}{\sqrt{0.505mL}} \\
c_3 &= \frac{1}{\sqrt{0.503mL}}
\end{align*}
$$

因此

$$w\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{W_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}$$

代入

$$m\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{W_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} + EI\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^4}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^4}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} = f(x,t)$$

所以

$$
m\int_0^L {{W_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{W_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} {\rm{d}}x + EI} \int_0^L {{W_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^4}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^4}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} {\rm{d}}x} = \int_0^L {{W_j}\left( x \right)f\left( {x,t} \right){\rm{d}}x}
$$

得

$$
\begin{align*}
\ddot{\eta}_i + \omega_i^2 \eta_i &= F_0 \int_0^L W_i(x) \delta \left( x - \frac{L}{2} \right) u(t) \, dx \\
&= F_0 W_i\left( \frac{L}{2} \right) u(t), \quad i = 1,2,3
\end{align*}
$$

即

$$
\begin{align*}
\ddot{\eta}_1 + \omega_1^2 \eta_1 &= F_0 W_1\left( \frac{L}{2} \right) u(t) \\
\ddot{\eta}_2 + \omega_2^2 \eta_2 &= F_0 W_2\left( \frac{L}{2} \right) u(t) \\
\ddot{\eta}_3 + \omega_3^2 \eta_3 &= F_0 W_3\left( \frac{L}{2} \right) u(t)
\end{align*}
$$

右边为常数，所以特解为

$$
\eta_i = \frac {F_0 W_i\left( \frac{L}{2} \right)}{\omega_i^2} u(t)
$$

即

$$
\begin{align*}
\eta_1 &=\frac {F_0 W_1\left( \frac{L}{2} \right)}{\omega_1^2} u(t) = \frac{{1.23846 \times {{10}^{ - 2}}{F_0}{L^4}}}{{EI\sqrt {mL} }}u(t)\\
\eta_2 &=\frac {F_0 W_2\left( \frac{L}{2} \right)}{\omega_2^2} u(t) = -\frac{{3.39772 \times {{10}^{ - 5}}{F_0}{L^4}}}{{EI\sqrt {mL} }}u(t)\\
\eta_3 &=\frac {F_0 W_3\left( \frac{L}{2} \right)}{\omega_3^2} u(t) = -\frac{{1.74908 \times {{10}^{ - 4}}{F_0}{L^4}}}{{EI\sqrt {mL} }}u(t)
\end{align*}
$$

代入$w\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{W_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}$即可
